en.LINKING_HELP:
If you do not see here your all selected beacons it means that not all beacons are linkable:

1. It is possible to link beacons of demand* cathegory with beacons of supply* cathegory.
2. Beacons from the same cathegory are not linkable.
3. You must be an author of supply cathegory beacon to link it.
4. You can link your supply cathegory beacon with any beacon of demand cathegory.
* Demand cathegory includes SOS, Good, Bad and Important beacon's types, supply cathegory includes Voting, Programm, Project, Project Proposal, Request and Participative Budget types.
